Here are fifteen popular tourist attractions in Zakopane, Poland:

1. Krupówki Street - Urban/Shopping
2. Gubałówka Hill - Nature/Viewpoint
3. Tatra National Park - Nature/Hiking
4. Morskie Oko Lake - Nature/Lake
5. Chochołowska Valley - Nature/Valley
6. Jaszczurówka Chapel on the Rock - Historical/Chapel
7. Wielka Krokiew Ski Jumping Center - Sports/Ski jumping center
8. Thermal Pools of Bukovina - Recreational/Thermal pools
9. Dunajec River Rafting Trips - Adventure/River rafting trips
10. The Museum of Zakopane Style "Koliba"- Cultural/Museum
11. Nosal Mountain Funicular Railway - Transportation/Funicular railway
12. Szymoszkowa Slope with ski lifts - Winter sports/Ski slope
13. Tatras Ethnographic Park - Culture/Ethnographic park
14. Kościeliska Valley - Nature/Valley
15. Willa Koliba - Architectural monument/Villa
